<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/mycokeys.82.66603.figure10>
    dc:description "Figure 10. Sporothrix undulata sp. nov. (CBS 147929) a ascoma b ascomatal base c ostiolar hyphae d asci e ascospores f-h globose conidia arising on long conidiophore or directly from hyphae i globose conidia j conidiogenous cell with an inflated cluster of denticles at the apex k conidia l-m fourteen-day-old culture on MEA (left- pigmented CBS 147929, right - white KFL 404 DB 16 bRJCU). Scale bars: 100 μm (a), 25 μm (b-d), 10 μm (e), 25 μm (f), 10 μm (g, h), 5 μm (i), 10 μm (j), 5 μm (k)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/574238" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

